					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">YY-CHR lets you horizontally move blocks of graphics very easily.<br />Where it says &quot;x8&quot; is the zoom setting.  Reduce this, and it fits more tiles into the editing area.<br />Get the editing area to be 32x32 pixels, then hit the &quot;Shift to Right&quot; button.  Instant shifted graphics.  Just need to copy paste a bunch of times, and hit it again.<br /><br />It's a two minute job to copy-paste-shift in YY-CHR.</div>

					
